# ── DashGo Mobile (Expo) — PRODUCTION ─────────────────────────────
# These vars are injected at build time by EAS. EAS_PROJECT_SECRETS take
# precedence over values in eas.json — set the sensitive ones with
# `eas secret:create` instead of committing them here.
#
# Non-sensitive (live in eas.json under the "production" profile):
#   EXPO_PUBLIC_API_URL=https://api.dashgo.dev/api
#
# Sensitive (live as EAS project secrets — never committed):
#   EXPO_PUBLIC_STRIPE_PUBLISHABLE_KEY=pk_live_...
#   EXPO_PUBLIC_SENTRY_DSN=https://<public_key>@o<org_id>.ingest.sentry.io/<project_id>
#
# To set the secrets:
#   eas secret:create --scope project --name EXPO_PUBLIC_STRIPE_PUBLISHABLE_KEY --value pk_live_xxx
#   eas secret:create --scope project --name EXPO_PUBLIC_SENTRY_DSN --value https://...
#
# To verify they're set:
#   eas secret:list
